      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just not the same though. everyone says it gets better with time but what if it doesn't? what if this is just how it is now? just this heavy, empty feeling forever. i feel like i'm just dragging this body around for no reason. like there's no point in even trying to get through the day if the person who made everything worth it is just gone. it's just so exhausting to exist like this.",
